{"tid":1630723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 反抗","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:02:08.000Z","uid":199793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18a6a4b929cc51507f9d635db0f6c950bd3ec5c7","tid":1630723,"uid":199793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"呢幾日，因為緊急法同蒙面法，令到<br />\n「<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黑色嚴重分化撚警告</strong></span></span>」持續生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家呢場運動已經發展到一個新階段，好多香港人都未經歷過呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地黎緊嘅每一步行動都要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>謹慎</strong></span></span>，因為行錯一步，結果就會變到而家嘅政府咁醜陋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無可否認，方向變得有D混亂，唔同人有唔同意見，但我地唔應該將自己變到同港共政府一樣，厚顏無恥。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個香港人，我地應該做一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有承擔</span></strong></span>嘅抗爭者，錯就要認，認左亦都唔夠，要有補救。如果唔係就同班垃圾狗官，保皇廢物一樣，咁撚仆街。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位香港人抗爭者未來之戰上<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>三思</strong>\b[size=5]</span>，[size=5]<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">謹慎</span></strong></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>承擔</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"704c8d3de9158df73e5dba23fb8180c32291d444","tid":1630723,"uid":199793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"仆街 size襟多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a6084547daaa17ec5c6749c5aad52158620f3d","tid":1630723,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"badfcf636cc72442489baa7adfafb42f0bcd59a1","tid":1630723,"uid":199793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"三樣野 三思，謹慎，承擔  手足們緊記<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30669fbc5cef40ae5384ee63faa3bfd110981f1f","tid":1630723,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"講左好多次口罩遮唔到幾多<br />\n要做事的話 最低消費帽+面巾<br />\n<br />\n［停一停諗一諗］花少少時間睇 你覺得政府係咪真係冇做野？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630572</a><br />\n<br />\n［花10秒睇保護自已］千祈唔好